(221, 1, '2020-03-21 15:28:46', '2020-03-21 15:28:46', '[vc_row use_container=\"yes\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1584806111490{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner][ts_about_text_content animate_block=\"yes\" animation_type=\"fadeInUp\"]\r\n<h2><em>Manufacturing</em>Excellence</h2>\r\n<h6>Top Grade Raw Materials</h6>\r\n[/ts_about_text_content][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1584806138319{margin-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" offset=\"vc_col-md-7\"][ts_about_text_content animate_block=\"yes\" animation_type=\"fadeInUp\"]When it comes to product quality, raw materials play a critical role. nepovit ceramics understands this concept very well, which is why we only use the highest quality, finest raw materials such as clay, calcium silicate slag, and others to produce the best ceramic tiles in the industry. All of the raw materials we use are sourced from places known for producing high-quality ceramic raw materials.\r\n\r\nWhen these materials arrive, they are thoroughly inspected and tested by a third-party lab. Furthermore, these raw materials are only used in production if all of the quality checks are passed. All of this effort and process is done solely to ensure that we produce and supply high-quality ceramic products worldwide. Ultimately, when you buy tiles from Nepovit ceramics, you can be certain of their quality.[/ts_about_text_content][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" offset=\"vc_col-md-5\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1584947844739{margin-bottom: 60px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner][ts_image_slider next=\"Next\" prev=\"Prev\" animate_block=\"yes\" animation_type=\"fadeInUp\" details=\"%5B%7B%22image%22%3A%22486%22%7D%2C%7B%22image%22%3A%22485%22%7D%5D\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Manufacturing Excellence', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'manufacturing-excellence', '', '', '2022-04-04 09:53:13', '2022-04-04 09:53:13', '', 0, 'http://hompark.themezinho.net/?page_id=221', 0, 'page', '', 0);
