(496, 1, '2022-04-04 10:02:24', '2022-04-04 10:02:24', '<p>[vc_row use_container=\"yes\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1584806111490{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner][ts_about_text_content animate_block=\"yes\" animation_type=\"fadeInUp\"]</p>\n<h2><em>About</em> Nepovit</h2>\n<h6>Artistic Impression With Marvellous Collection.</h6>\n<p>[/ts_about_text_content][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1584806138319{margin-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" offset=\"vc_col-md-7\"][ts_about_text_content animate_block=\"yes\" animation_type=\"fadeInUp\"]Headquartered in the nepal– the ceramic hub of Nepal, Nepovit one of nepal\'s fastest-growing first ceramic company. Founded in 2022, the firm is well-equipped with cutting-edge technology, solid infrastructure, and a highly qualified team of experts.<br />\nIn the coming years, the company aspires to be a global leader in the ceramic industry by producing high-quality tiles and other ceramic products.[/ts_about_text_content][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" offset=\"vc_col-md-5\"][ts_about_text_content animate_block=\"yes\" animation_type=\"fadeInUp\" animation_delay=\"0.05s\"]As a result, we also spend a significant amount of money on research, innovation and training. Currently, the company is able to produce 20,000 to 30,000 square metres of tiles per day.[/ts_about_text_content][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1584947844739{margin-bottom: 60px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner][ts_image_slider next=\"Next\" prev=\"Prev\" animate_block=\"yes\" animation_type=\"fadeInUp\" details=\"%5B%7B%22image%22%3A%22491%22%7D%2C%7B%22image%22%3A%22492%22%7D%2C%7B%22image%22%3A%22493%22%7D%5D\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1584806158368{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][ts_about_text_content animate_block=\"yes\" animation_type=\"fadeInUp\"]</p>\n<h5>Our Vision</h5>\n<p>Our vision is to take the ceramics industry to new heights through product innovation. Furthermore, we are committed to making ceramic products as affordable as possible so that the majority of people can benefit from them.</p>\n<p>With an excellent manufacturing setup, a skilled workforce, and a clear vision, we are confident that we will be able to achieve this goal very soon.[/ts_about_text_content][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][ts_about_text_content animate_block=\"yes\" animation_type=\"fadeInUp\"]</p>\n<h5>Our Mission</h5>\n<p>Our mission is to revolutionise the ceramic industry by bringing major innovation and changing the way it operates. We are constantly striving to create high-quality, innovative ceramic products that will transform the way tiles are used in the future.</p>\n<p>We are focusing our efforts on two major areas: innovation and quality. We are optimistic that we will be successful in this mission very soon.[/ts_about_text_content][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner offset=\"vc_col-md-8\"][ts_video_content animate_block=\"yes\" animation_type=\"fadeInUp\" video_url=\"https://nepovit.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Video-Post.mp4\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>\n', 'About Nepovit', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '241-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-04-04 10:02:24', '2022-04-04 10:02:24', '', 241, 'http://nepovit.com/?p=496', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
