imate_block=\"yes\" animation_type=\"fadeInUp\"]The main objective of this examination is to timely apply corrective actions if needed. In addition, DPI gives you the opportunity to do improvements in quality.</p>\n<p>1. This inspection service verifies the entire production process in detail<br />\n2. Re-assure that Required Quality Parameters are Maintained or not<br />\n3. Keep control of the production process<br />\n4. Take corrective actions if needed<br />\n5. Assure that the mass production quality is the same as the master sample<br />\n6. Benefits of During production Inspection (DPI INSPECTION)<br />\n7. It Prevents expansion of faults moving into full production[/ts_side_text_left][/vc_column][vc_column offset=\"vc_col-md-6\"][ts_tab_content animate_block=\"yes\" animation_type=\"fadeInUp\" details=\"%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%2224324234%22%2C%22image%22%3A%2299%22%7D%5D\" title=\"76iuyuwe\" description=\"9879789\" icon=\"96\" image=\"146\" title1=\"600 X 600\" image1=\"477\" title2=\"600 X 1200\" image2=\"478\" image3=\"171\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row section_ratio=\"0.2\" motts_theme_padding=\"no\" use_container=\"yes\" section_background_image=\"514\" css=\".vc_custom_1649326898428{margin-bottom: 100px !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"2/3\" offset=\"vc_col-md-6\"][ts_consultation_box animate_block=\"yes\" animation_type=\"fadeInUp\" index=\"06\" title=\"Pre Shipment Inspection\"]Pre-shipment inspection is the final line of defense before a low-quality product leaves the factory Premise.</p>\n<p>Pre-Shipment Inspection (PSI), also known as Final Random Inspection (FRI), checks your finished products in order to assess problems with finished and packaged goods. This procedure is done through randomly selected pieces/boxes from Produced Goods and each piece/box is carefully examined in order to ensure it meets the Buyer’s expectations or not. the PSI ensures that the products comply with your specifications including overall appearance, size, color, sharpness, packing, labeling, etc.[/ts_consultation_box][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row use_container=\"yes\"][vc_column][ts_section_title align=\"center\" title=\"Our Catalouge\"][vc_column_text]</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Check and Download Our different designs Catalog</p>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title=\"Check Catalouge\" align=\"center\" css=\".vc_custom_1649327417674{border-top-width: 10px !important;padding-top: 10px !important;}\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row content_placement=\"middle\" use_container=\"yes\"][vc_column offset=\"vc_col-md-4\"][ts_section_title animate_block=\"yes\" animation_type=\"fadeInUp\" index=\"07\" title=\"<em>Nepovit</em> Certificates\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\" offset=\"vc_col-md-2 vc_col-xs-6\"][ts_certificates fancybox=\"yes\" animate_block=\"yes\" animation_type=\"fadeInUp\" image=\"420\" title=\"Certificate\" animation_delay=\"0s\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\" offset=\"vc_col-md-2 vc_col-xs-6\"][ts_certificates fancybox=\"yes\" animate_block=\"yes\" animation_type=\"fadeInUp\" image=\"419\" title=\"Certificate\" animation_delay=\"0.05s\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\" offset=\"vc_col-md-2 vc_col-xs-6\"][ts_certificates fancybox=\"yes\" animate_block=\"yes\" animation_type=\"fadeInUp\" image=\"418\" title=\"Certificate\" animation_delay=\"0.10s\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\" offset=\"vc_col-md-2 vc_col-xs-6\"][ts_certificates fancybox=\"yes\" animate_block=\"yes\" animation_type=\"fadeInUp\" image=\"417\" title=\"Certificate\" animation_delay=\"0.15s\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>\n', 'Start', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '427-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-04-07 11:25:14', '2022-04-07 11:25:14', '', 427, 'https://nepovit.com/?p=535', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
